flowchart TD

    A([Start]) --> B[Open Spiritual AI Chat Bot App]

    B --> C{User Registered?}

    C -- No --> D[Signup]
    D --> E[Create Account in Database]
    E --> F[Login]

    C -- Yes --> F

    F --> G{Valid Credentials?}

    G -- No --> H[Show Error Message]
    H --> F

    G -- Yes --> I[Generate JWT Token]
    I --> J[Open Dashboard]

    J --> K{Choose Action}

    K --> L[Start Chat]
    K --> M[View Chat History]
    K --> N[Voice Query]
    K --> O[Profile Settings]
    K --> P[Logout]

    L --> Q[Enter Spiritual Question]
    Q --> R[Send Request to AI Engine]
    R --> S[Generate Response]
    S --> T[Display Answer]
    T --> U[Save Chat in Database]
    U --> J

    M --> V[Fetch Previous Chats]
    V --> W[Display History]
    W --> J

    N --> X[Record Voice Input]
    X --> Y[Convert Speech to Text]
    Y --> R

    O --> Z[Update Profile]
    Z --> J

    P --> AA[Destroy Session Token]
    AA --> AB([End])

    J --> AC{Admin User?}

    AC -- Yes --> AD[Open Admin Dashboard]
    AD --> AE[View Users]
    AD --> AF[Monitor Chats]
    AD --> AG[Analytics Reports]

    AE --> J
    AF --> J
    AG --> J

    AC -- No --> J